Title: I Am Forsaken
Description:
We have fought to win back our home. We have fought to keep it safe. 

Your courage and strength are inspirational to the Forsaken. And with you, we know we have our champion. 

Go, they want to see you.
ObjectivesText: Receive the honor and accolades of the Forsaken.

Objectives.Text: Receive the Honor of the Forsaken
